<section>
    <header>
        <h1 class="sdst-heading">Modals</h1>
    </header>
    <div>
        <div class="sprk-c-Modal">
            <header class="sprk-c-Modal__header">
                <h2 class="sprk-b-Heading sprk-b-Heading--secondary">Are you sure?</h2>
            </header>
            <div class="sprk-c-Modal__body">
                <p>If you decline you will not be able to use MyQL to process your loan. All documents and signatures will need to be sent via postal mail which could delay your loan process.</p>
            </div>
            <footer class="sprk-c-Modal__footer">
                <ul class="sprk-c-ButtonSecondaryAction">
                    <li class="sprk-c-ButtonSecondaryAction__button">
                        <button class="sprk-c-Button sprk-c-Button--primary">Confirm</button>
                    </li>
                    <li class="sprk-c-ButtonSecondaryAction__link"><a href="">Cancel</a></li>
                </ul>
            </footer>
        </div>
        <div class="sprk-c-ModalMask"></div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <div class="sprk-c-Modal">
            <div class="sprk-c-Modal__header">
                <h2 class="sprk-b-Heading sprk-b-Heading--secondary">Please wait while we do something</h2>
                <div class="sprk-c-Modal__spinner">
                    <span class="sprk-c-Spinner sprk-c-Spinner--circle sprk-c-Spinner--large"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sprk-c-Modal__body">
                <p><strong>Sit tight! This may take a few minutes!</strong></p>
                <p>If you decline you will not be able to use MyQL to process your loan. All documents and signatures will need to be sent via postal mail which could delay your loan process.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sprk-c-ModalMask"></div>
    </div>
</section>